\" style=\"height:365px; width:660px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://demo4-cgroup.top/local/storage/app/public/images/images/d%E1%BB%B1%20%C3%A1n%20ti%C3%AAu%20bi%E1%BB%83u/b%E1%BA%A5t%20%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng%20s%E1%BA%A3n/v%E1%BA%ADn%20t%E1%BA%A3i/C360_2016-11-16-13-40-47-354-660x365.jpg\" style=\"height:365px; width:660px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://demo4-cgroup.top/local/storage/app/public/images/images/d%E1%BB%B1%20%C3%A1n%20ti%C3%AAu%20bi%E1%BB%83u/b%E1%BA%A5t%20%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng%20s%E1%BA%A3n/v%E1%BA%ADn%20t%E1%BA%A3i/C360_2016-11-16-13-40-56-822-660x365.jpg\" style=\"height:365px; width:660px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://demo4-cgroup.top/local/storage/app/public/images/images/d%E1%BB%B1%20%C3%A1n%20ti%C3%AAu%20bi%E1%BB%83u/b%E1%BA%A5t%20%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng%20s%E1%BA%A3n/v%E1%BA%ADn%20t%E1%BA%A3i/C360_2016-11-16-13-41-13-963-660x365.jpg\" style=\"height:365px; width:660px\" /></p>', 'tham-dinh-gia-o-to-tai-ninh-binh'),
(5, '2018-10-12 21:07:52', '2018-10-12 21:07:52', 'Thẩm định giá phương tiện vận tải tại Hưng Yên', '15394036721-2.jpg', '<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://demo4-cgroup.top/local/storage/app/public/images/images/d%E1%BB%B1%20%C3%A1n%20ti%C3%AAu%20bi%E1%BB%83u/b%E1%BA%A5t%20%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng%20s%E1%BA%A3n/v%E1%BA%ADn%20t%E1%BA%A3i/1-2-574x365.png\" style=\"height:365px; width:574px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Phương tiện vận tải</strong>&nbsp;:02 &Ocirc; t&ocirc;<br />\r\n<strong>Địa điểm</strong>&nbsp;: Hưng Y&ecirc;n<br />\r\n<strong>H&atilde;ng</strong>&nbsp;: SAMCO<br />\r\n<strong>Mục đ&iacute;ch thẩm định gi&aacute;</strong>&nbsp;: B&aacute;n đấu gi&aacute; t&agrave;i sản<br />\r\n<strong>Ph&aacute;p l&yacute;</strong>&nbsp;: Đầy đủ<br />\r\n<strong>Thời gian</strong>: Th&aacute;ng 02/2017</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://demo4-cgroup.top/local/storage/app/public/images/images/d%E1%BB%B1%20%C3%A1n%20ti%C3%AAu%20bi%E1%BB%83u/b%E1%BA%A5t%20%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng%20s%E1%BA%A3n/v%E1%BA%ADn%20t%E1%BA%A3i/2-2-559x365.png\" style=\"height:365px; width:559px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://demo4-cgroup.top/local/storage/app/public/images/images/d%E1%BB%B1%20%C3%A1n%20ti%C3%AAu%20bi%E1%BB%83u/b%E1%BA%A5t%20%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng%20s%E1%BA%A3n/v%E1%BA%ADn%20t%E1%BA%A3i/3-1-588x365.png\" style=\"height:365px; width:588px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://demo4-cgroup.top/local/storage/app/public/images/images/d%E1%BB%B1%20%C3%A1n%20ti%C3%AAu%20bi%E1%BB%83u/b%E1%BA%A5t%20%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng%20s%E1%BA%A3n/v%E1%BA%ADn%20t%E1%BA%A3i/5-557x365.png\" style=\"height:365px; width:557px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://demo4-cgroup.top/local/storage/app/public/images/images/d%E1%BB%B1%20%C3%A1n%20ti%C3%AAu%20bi%E1%BB%83u/b%E1%BA%A5t%20%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng%20s%E1%BA%A3n/v%E1%BA%ADn%20t%E1%BA%A3i/6-600x365.png\" style=\"height:365px; width:600px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://demo4-cgroup.top/local/storage/app/public/images/images/d%E1%BB%B1%20%C3%A1n%20ti%C3%AAu%20bi%E1%BB%83u/b%E1%BA%A5t%20%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng%20s%E1%BA%A3n/v%E1%BA%ADn%20t%E1%BA%A3i/4-636x365.png\" style=\"height:365px; width:636px\" /></p>', 'tham-dinh-gia-phuong-tien-van-tai-tai-hung-yen');

